OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItaly ex-PM Berlusconi     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Freappears following illness
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Italy's former prime minister Silvio   
OL,6, Berlusconi has told supporters he's    
OL,7, ready to go back to work after a month 
OL,8, in hospital.                           
OL,10,FThe 86-year-old, who is suffering from 
OL,11,Fleukaemia, was rushed into intensive   
OL,12,Fcare with a related lung infection but 
OL,13,Fhis condition has since stabilised.    
OL,15,FThere has been no word on when he might
OL,16,Fleave hospital.                        
OL,18,FIn a video address from his room, Mr   
OL,19,FBerlusconi thanked his Forza Italia    
OL,20,Fparty members for their support.       
